  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what they did was to-- and this was done through the help of the officers at Wiesbaden and also Lord Justice Wright, who was the Lord Chancellor of England.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got together, and they decided on, all right, we can come within the ambit of a common design, and common design to subject these prisoners to beatings, tortures, killings, starvation.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was a common intent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an intent on the part of those people who operated these camps, from the kommandant down to the kapo, including the guards, to subject these prisoners to extermination, ultimately, where there were Jews.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews were not-- they were singled out for extermination, but they were not the only prisoners in the camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were-- actually, when Hitler overran a country, the first thing he did was to collect up the intelligentsia of that country and those who were in authority and those who really were the brains of that particular country that had been overrun and haul them off to concentration camps for protective custody.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that-- you-- we had to have a charge that was broad enough to encompass all these different activities and yet be narrow enough to put them on notice of what it was they were being tried for.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aiding, abetting, and furthering anyone who participated to the extent of giving aid or abetting or furthering the plan or scheme to subject these prisoners to beatings, killings, and tortures would be within the ambit of the charge.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You are indeed a participant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to have a concept that you would be principals in the first, second degree, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was abolished by federal statute.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
